---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title="About | Hexaxia Labs" description="Hexaxia Labs is the open source arm of the Hexaxia Group, where work from Hexaxia Technologies, Hexaxia AI, and Hexaxia Media goes when it is general enough to share." />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16">
      <header class="mb-12 pb-8 border-b border-[#1E2028]">
        <p class="font-mono text-xs text-[#6B7280] tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">About</p>
        <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold text-[#E8E4D8] tracking-tight">Hexaxia Labs</h1>
      </header>
      <div class="prose">
        <p>
          Hexaxia Labs is the open source arm of the <a href="https://www.hexaxia.com">Hexaxia Group</a>,
          a collective of operating companies.
          <a href="https://www.hexaxia.tech">Hexaxia Technologies</a> does managed IT,
          infrastructure, and security consulting.
          <a href="https://www.hexaxia.ai">Hexaxia AI</a> runs AI transformation engagements
          and builds AI infrastructure products.
          <a href="https://www.hexaxia.media">Hexaxia Media</a> handles the creative and media
          side of the group.
        </p>
        <p>
          Each division does different work. Some of it is client-specific.
          Some of it is not. Labs is where the second kind lives.
        </p>
        <p>
          The projects here grow out of real work across the group:
          hardening production systems, building compliance baselines, shipping
          tooling that solves problems we actually have, and integrating AI into
          infrastructure that has to stay accountable.
          When something is general enough to be useful outside our own operation,
          we open source it.
        </p>
        <p>
          Projects live at <a href="https://github.com/Hexaxia-Labs">github.com/Hexaxia-Labs</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
